{"tid":2327614,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不只航海王！「幽遊白書」確定開拍真人版　男主角鎖定他們","createTime":"2020-12-16T07:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T15:42:24.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a9f7fc13537fb7d7cb99b781349d35ab255c1d2b","tid":2327614,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:40:38.000Z","msg":"Netflix平台大動作投資改版日本經典漫畫！先前宣布《航海王》開拍真人版後，近日《今際之國的闖關者》更獲得大成功之後，現在證實要將拍攝《幽遊白書》真人版，裡頭的角色選擇再度受矚目，演出《今際之國的闖關者》山崎賢人也點名再度挑大樑！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/12/16/2938273-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F12%2F16%2F2938273-PH.jpg&h=cae760d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲經典漫畫《幽遊白書》是不少漫畫迷的回憶。（圖／翻攝自《幽遊白書：BANG！靈丸》手遊）<br />\n<br />\n經典日本漫畫《幽遊白書》曾拍攝過電視與電影動畫，該作品是漫畫作家冨樫義博在1990年代的經典代表作品，講述14歲少年浦飯幽助因一場車禍事故，被任命為解決與妖怪案有關的靈界偵探，而發生一連串連結人間與靈界的故事。曾拍成電視動畫，更推出兩部電影動畫片，最近更有真人舞台劇演出，不過從未改編成真人版電影或戲劇。<br />\n<br />\n今（16）日Netflix宣布要將《幽遊白書》改編成真人版影集，預計在全球190國上架，由坂本和隆擔任執行製作，並由最近才剛於Netflix上線的《今際之國的闖關者》製作公司ROBOT負責，消息一出讓6、7年級們漫畫迷無不嗨翻天，粉絲更馬上敲碗點名「菅田將暉、綾野剛、賀來賢人、北村匠海」等新生代性格男星主演。"},{"pid":"8f28f95f889fd9defb987ceb1de1a1e83181b62b","tid":2327614,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:44:21.000Z","msg":"哈啊～<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88029ed55a1da8c97555b40b3cea730a8b48fd18","tid":2327614,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"邊個做戶愚呂弟 仙水"},{"pid":"b955b8d3e0528b950bd83d0312d971d03f7dc198","tid":2327614,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"88029ed55a1da8c97555b40b3cea730a8b48fd18","tid":2327614,"uid":139228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"邊個做戶愚呂弟 仙水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:50:26.000Z","msg":"仙水應該係同性戀黑人<br />\n<br />\n戶禺呂oversize變性人"},{"pid":"d77f6ac99411b11f640e34692d6e72a1e284a9cc","tid":2327614,"uid":48187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:58:07.000Z","msg":"慘遭真人化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4517c86926b57aa64e3096abacfc01a360c0ab86","tid":2327614,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T13:37:31.000Z","msg":"幻海應該係女角......"},{"pid":"590780c04a6dc77ff4e747c102770f5be2c0f41f","tid":2327614,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"山崎賢人咩漫畫主角都演到勁撚屈.."},{"pid":"d842a276e155498780aaf8e6985ea44141789154","tid":2327614,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"590780c04a6dc77ff4e747c102770f5be2c0f41f","tid":2327614,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"山崎賢人咩漫畫主角都演到勁撚屈.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"佢個樣本身就似漫畫男主角feel"},{"pid":"1d46cbc78cdf45abf287e7bc22a08801984aef1d","tid":2327614,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"北村匠海係咪做怪獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}